  <entry>
    <title>各图床的对比，来看看哪个图床更好用</title>
    <link href="/2024/02/09/%E9%85%B7%E5%AE%89/"/>
    <url>/2024/02/09/%E9%85%B7%E5%AE%89/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>由于自己搭的网盘有点拉跨，导致我的图床时不时抽风，故决定寻找稳定的第三方图床</p><h2 id="酷安"><a href="#酷安" class="headerlink" title="酷安"></a>酷安</h2><p>偶然间发现酷安也能做图床，而且效果还不错，不知道有没有防盗链</p><p><img src="https://image.coolapk.com/picture/2022/1101/18/22695963_17914b08_7090_8248_5@2560x1440.jpeg.m.jpg"></p><img title="" src="https://image.coolapk.com/feed/2024/0207/22/3121641_198cccad_5208_458_254@1920x1080.gif" alt="" data-align="inline"><h2 id="Github图床"><a href="#Github图床" class="headerlink" title="Github图床"></a>Github图床</h2><p>这个应该是知名度较高的了，搭配picgo使用体验也还可以，下面放几张图</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/morannlx/Picturebed/test.png"></p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/morannlx/Picturebed/c26c962279a5789b0ad573aa8c2f5fe0.jpg"></p><h2 id="QQ空间"><a href="#QQ空间" class="headerlink" title="QQ空间"></a>QQ空间</h2><p>这个也算一种比较稳定的方案，但是由于压缩，图片会比较糊</p><p><img src="http://photogz.photo.store.qq.com/psc?/V13C7ML60byvuj/ruAMsa53pVQWN7FLK88i5k1UiRCnURX5qFG5hsAFmBL.eurkIz*iiS3uss00H0oyJxHBRlboM2.qL91lPJ9GX9Jo4jBIbPZh3H9.P2M6514!/mnull&bo=gAc4BIAHOAQDCSw!&rf=photolist&t=5"></p><p>暂时先写到这，后面会持续更新</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>Git 本地与GitHub远程同步</title>
    <link href="/2023/10/03/git/"/>
    <url>/2023/10/03/git/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="基本步骤："><a href="#基本步骤：" class="headerlink" title="基本步骤："></a>基本步骤：</h3><p>本地添加仓库：</p><p>创建文件夹</p><p>打开git</p><p>初始化仓库</p><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs csharp">git <span class="hljs-keyword">init</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置提交代码时的用户信息：</p><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs stylus">git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.name</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;morannlx&quot;</span><br>git config <span class="hljs-attr">--global</span> user<span class="hljs-selector-class">.email</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;2152533805@qq.com&quot;</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建立本地仓库与远程仓库的链接：</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">git remote -v</span> <br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>新建远程仓库连接</p><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs mipsasm">git remote <span class="hljs-keyword">add </span><span class="hljs-keyword">origin </span>[远程仓库连接地址]<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c">git remote rm origin [远程仓库连接地址]   <span class="hljs-comment">//解除连接</span><br><br>git pull origin main<span class="hljs-comment">//拉取同步文件</span><br><br>git add . <span class="hljs-comment">//添加需要同步上传的文件 . 表示上传全部</span><br><br>git commit -m <span class="hljs-string">&quot;备注说明”</span><br><br>git push origin main<span class="hljs-comment">//开始进行push，弹出GitHub登录窗口，输入注册的GitHub账号即可</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="其他指令："><a href="#其他指令：" class="headerlink" title="其他指令："></a>其他指令：</h3><p>查看git仓库中各文件状态</p><figure class="highlight ebnf"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ebnf"><span class="hljs-attribute">git status</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>git删除文件夹：</p><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs maxima">git rm [文件名] -r -f<br>git commit -m &#x27;<span class="hljs-built_in">del</span> config&#x27; <br>git <span class="hljs-built_in">push</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">origin</span> main<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看日志：</p><figure class="highlight 1c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs 1c">git <span class="hljs-built_in">log</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改仓库名：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">git branch -M <span class="hljs-selector-tag">main</span><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
